You need to move the declaration (i.e. the following portion) to rational.h:
```
class Rational{
public:

    void reduce(int n, int d);
    //define math functions
    void add(int n, int d);
    void sub(int n, int d);
    void div(int n, int d);
    void mul(int n, int d);
};

```
For more information, see [this question][1].


