Looks like this is the problem:

        setUnlocalizedName(name);
        setRegistryName(name);

There, `name` is `&quot;netherinium_sword&quot;`. Your unlocalized name and registry name aren&#39;t supposed to be the same, as your registry name needs to be namespaced. Try this instead:

        setUnlocalizedName(name);
        setRegistryName(&quot;mcadditions:&quot; + name);

(Or if you have a constant with your mod ID, you can use it instead of hardcoding.)

